WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.550 --> 00:00:03.668
Almost every app needs
a way to store data.

00:00:03.668 --> 00:00:06.980
It maybe as simple as
a few user preferences or

00:00:06.980 --> 00:00:10.140
more complex relational datasets.

00:00:10.140 --> 00:00:11.280
Because of this,

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:16.430
there isn't a one size fits all storage
mechanism that works in all cases.

00:00:16.430 --> 00:00:20.410
Let's take a look at a few different
techniques that you can use and

00:00:20.410 --> 00:00:22.450
their advantages and disadvantages.

